OL,3,CProtest held in Strabane over fuel cost
OL,5,FA small slow-moving protest has taken
OL,6,Fplace in Strabane over the soaring
OL,7,Fprice of fuel and cost of living.
OL,9,FAround 20 vehicles took part in the
OL,10,Fplanned convoy through the town on
OL,11,FSaturday afternoon.
OL,13,FPolice and the Parades Commission were
OL,14,Faware of the peaceful demonstration.
OL,16,FThose taking part in the convoy were
OL,17,Ffrom the farming and haulage industry.
OL,18,FThey say doing business is getting
OL,19,Falmost impossible.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
