OL,3,CProtest held in Strabane over fuel cost
OL,5,F"It's not just about the price of
OL,6,Ffuel, it's about the price of
OL,7,Feverything, it's about the cost of
OL,8,Fliving and how people are getting
OL,9,Fimpacted across our society,"
OL,10,Fconstruction worker Michael McLaughlin
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"Every time you go out the front door
OL,14,Fpeople are getting asked to dig deeper
OL,15,Fand they dont have the money to do it."
